vacay fit day one 👒🕶️☀️

kept it super simple & casual - a lightweight top, straight fit pants & sneakers that survived all the walking we did 😅

It was hot (as expected) so I didn’t want to fuss with anything tight or too “styled”. Just threw this on and it worked - breathable, comfy & easy to move around in while we explored, grabbed food & wandered into random cute spots. 

Honestly, this kind of outfit is my go-to when I’m travelling - something that feels good to wear and doesn’t need constant adjusting or second-guessing!

It effortlessly dissolves stubborn waterproof mascara, lifts away sunscreen & even all the population & dirt after a long day. After rinsing, my skin feels fresh, comfortable & clean, that’s perfect for layering my serums & moisturisers.
